{"tid":1960947,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國外交政策智庫：中共隱瞞疫情　英國應告上國際法庭　追討3.3萬億港元損失","createTime":"2020-04-06T12:38:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T14:36:12.000Z","uid":125168,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"dc65a934d87a1ecb6e8ce7a7272ba3e6ffbc29d0","tid":1960947,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T12:38:51.000Z","msg":"英國外交政策智庫：中共隱瞞疫情　英國應告上國際法庭　追討3.3萬億港元損失<br />\n<br />\n眾新聞：<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/28639/%E6%B5%B7%E7%89%99%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E6%B3%95%E5%BA%AD-28639/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96%E6%99%BA%E5%BA%AB%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E9%9A%B1%E7%9E%9E%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%87%89%E5%91%8A%E4%B8%8A%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E6%B3%95%E5%BA%AD-%E8%BF%BD%E8%A8%8E33%E8%90%AC%E5%84%84%E6%B8%AF%E5%85%83%E6%90%8D%E5%A4%B1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F28639%2F%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E7%2589%2599%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BA%25AD-28639%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A4%2596%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%2594%25BF%25E7%25AD%2596%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%25BA%25AB%25EF%25BC%259A%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25B1%25E9%259A%25B1%25E7%259E%259E%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%2591%258A%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BA%25AD-%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E8%25A8%258E33%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2584%2584%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%2590%258D%25E5%25A4%25B1&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLVBOXtrJgaeu%2B3uDm9UxZFo%3D&h=241d23e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/28639/%E6%B5%B7%E7%89%99%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E6%B3%95%E5%BA%AD-28639/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96%E6%99%BA%E5%BA%AB%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E9%9A%B1%E7%9E%9E%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%87%89%E5%91%8A%E4%B8%8A%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E6%B3%95%E5%BA%AD-%E8%BF%BD%E8%A8%8E33%E8%90%AC%E5%84%84%E6%B8%AF%E5%85%83%E6%90%8D%E5%A4%B1</a><br />\n<br />\n英國外交政策智庫組織「亨利傑克遜學會」( Henry Jackson Society，下稱HJS) 昨日（5日）發表報告，就中共政府隱瞞新冠肺炎訊息所造成的政策失誤，應如何賠償英國及多個發達經濟體的經濟損失。報告指，中共並未從沙士疫情中汲取教訓，對WHO及外界發布錯誤資訊，指中共已違反國際法，損害多國經濟，應向英國賠償 3,510億英鎊 (約3.3萬億港元)及向七大工業國集團（G7）賠償巨額損失。<br />\n<br />\n該報告題為《新冠病毒補償？評估中國潛在過失和法律索償研究》，指中國顯然違反《國際衛生條例》，該條約屬控制傳染病於全球蔓延的國際條約，中國屬簽署國之一，受國際法規管。若從法律途徑追討，英國賠償額則高達 3,510億英鎊 (約3.3萬億港元)，單是G7 賠償金額高達3.2萬億英鎊，並講解10種控告中國的法律途徑。<br />\n<br />\n報告亦包括15名保守黨成員建議，<span style=\"color: red;\">指首相約翰遜（Boris Johnson）應重新檢視英中關係。</span>"},{"pid":"131a0ad33faa1df2580d0cad4bccd43548c74543","tid":1960947,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T12:41:14.000Z","msg":"工黨奶共d 定保守黨奶共d ?"},{"pid":"6e8c257de3e431992a9d58b4b435ad611058d5dd","tid":1960947,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T12:41:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f15fb648d1e26c21efd0dcca330af96da5838212","tid":1960947,"uid":130419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T12:42:18.000Z","msg":"仲有大把國家奶"},{"pid":"f932914cc316f7797d5e21b7407bf3d135f06f54","tid":1960947,"uid":124806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T12:43:12.000Z","msg":"應該拎返香港當抵償啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b5510c2fe5d4792df2e1450e38821a820de